 "ἀθέτησις": "<b>ἀθέτησις, εως, ἡ</b> : <span style='color:red'>Nom</span>, <span style='color:red'>Féminin</span><br><u>EN 1</u> : a setting aside<br><u>EN 2</u> : annulment, nullification, abrogation.<br><u>FR 1</u> : <font color='blue'>une mise de côté</font><br><u>FR 2</u> : annulation, annulation, abrogation.",
